This is a basic application that takes input from a Wii classic controller connected to A2-A5 analog inputs and outputs different Super Mario Bros sound effects by a Piezo speaker connected to pin 12.

Hardware used:
 - Arduino Uno R3
 - Standard Piezo speaker
 - Nunchucky (https://www.adafruit.com/products/345)

Code credits:
 - Notes.h                               Arduino.cc
 - Code for melody creation (Modified)   Arduino.cc
 - WiiClasic.h (Modified)                Tim Hirzel (http://growdown.blogspot.com/)
